Saggy tits" is a casual term for sagging breasts, which is medically called breast ptosis.

Common causes include:

Aging
Pregnancy and breastfeeding (pregnancy itself is a major factor)
Weight gain and weight loss
Genetics
Larger breast size
Loss of skin elasticity over time
Smoking (can reduce skin elasticity)

It is very common and completely normal. Sagging does not usually indicate a medical problem or affect breast health.

